          <definition xml:id="def-topological-space"><title>Topological Space</title>
            <statement>
              <p>
                A topological space is an ordered pair <m>(ğ‘‹, ğ’¯)</m>, where <m>ğ‘‹</m> is a set and <m>ğ’¯</m> is a topology on <m>ğ‘‹</m>.
