                Let X be a topological space and suppose that X = âˆªÎ± UÎ± with each UÎ± open in X. Let each UÎ± have the subspace topology from X. If f: X â†’ Y is a function satisfying f|UÎ±: UÎ± â†’ Y is continuous for all Î±, then f is continuous.
